      "body" : "That's why I put \"address reuse\", I agree with not reusing addresses, however you can't control what the users request withdrawing to (they're free to withdraw to any address they want).\r\n\r\nThis feature request was more implying a functionality that's available through bitcoin-tx but not on bitcoin-cli (RPC). One of the proposed solution (add a new method) doesn't break anything and add the posibility to run the exact command from bitcoin-tx.",
